 to facilitate low-latency communication between GPUs and quantum processors. Well-funded companies in the quantum space include PsiQuantum, SandboxAQ, Quantinuum, and IQM Quantum Computers.\n\nIn the next 12 months, the trend is expected to shift from pilot projects to broader implementation, with more accessible quantum-as-a-service platforms. This will likely include the integration of quantum algorithms into mainstream AI frameworks such as TensorFlow and PyTorch."}],"role":"model"},"finish_reason":"STOP","grounding_metadata":{"grounding_chunks":[{"web":{"title":"iankhan.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE-UFunXH657cWiLOuQGYN6jYDmss6-vv4UhoJuDthtxyNYrsr9Ove6qCaNS4Hk_JZCQLYn89AwjmYeMWp2sqoYCsTbRYyqv0KUAicK102f7VJdx4uUzpxXNT-nVzRTlNeBccFT8u-d2bT1FMh31owGk0fq_WHxO1PDk3KwPneMeDWwNL-5ADuc59Qlt1PrJuZQc_HoqM0ICA_TRsZ_b4gxyi78uOlC6TNeHKTbp_llt6yMF7U="}},{"web":{"title":"bqpsim.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGKlvZqT-b37UNmoOWaxh8G21Xkzu0L1uKL3YEq5ap5sUpIpj9WFg2SS0q9uwApuSf1RHSlRBlsK9dL5VgpUqTKGaWyfE_KakrYNbKZsJ9mooWk9TnbdQmRZSV1kY1QZjMeOA9PvlmsgrbL2YRC7evmq7kC-JTxc-1D2Wl0V7csJ_Y="}},{"web":{"title":"usdsi.org","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHzD7uMKz9atpQXVkmhwicTLE4OGxS1Wm1lAZ_4rDF_tW7bJI09fdi1xtEW-xjEqcmkYOweMOqs9dx-XPZra_uVI8dixSodPzvi_etjwLZfi-RC3WvaQ5jBa1si0vQjS74thWGknptp1mM2itVR9PBdqHagTnnTLrxbtMVzTCqTZEgGPbwTRlwvBfCRcfdwyrqPbJGmI5G7L1ZmlhoH"}},{"web":{"title":"vivatech.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGS_Yy5mn8Q4RgL1W1E1MXndbX9Ck2uRthDqs24LiCoi6xxGmY07g9t0C5ZGJ7B25nHYIOZ79Imraip9r2GybXIUr1bKrEs1EXhdggT2ekizLRzicltWdhxlZ9_00zXVN-Xc72SCtjqffBA-3w1bkSJQNSpxFrqrbhl8iXuwXPuyJMh4uZUZvnsfymVVjOpgOOjWG3wbN1l75Ht"}},{"web":{"title":"ai-supremacy.com","uri":"https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFfJOwdBrLmuorJlwiErMr41KRMghmUNQGebX0tjE2ai67mkXuRU8Yklr0KR3Oq